</pre></div>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id="Variants">Variants</h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Fisher%E2%80%93Yates_shuffle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: Variants"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id="Sattolo's_algorithm"><span id="Sattolo.27s_algorithm"></span>Sattolo's algorithm</h3><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Fisher%E2%80%93Yates_shuffle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: Sattolo&#039;s algorithm"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
